580
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,200
You don't have to do this!

581
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,640
You don't have to do this!

582
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:51,800
Let us go!

583
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,200
I confess!

584
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,120
It's all me!

585
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,560
I'll give you anything!

586
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:01,840
The locker

587
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,560
(Locker that contains the proof)
contains proof of your crimes.

588
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:06,000
Repent before you die.

589
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:15,000
Here.

590
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,200
Read your own crimes out aloud.

591
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:16,680
Take it.

592
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:18,600
(Detective speaks)
Alright, start reading.

593
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:19,080
Fine.

594
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,680
An Glass Factory

595
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:22,560
new material usage agreement.

596
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:23,520
I, Jin Xiangyu,

597
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,080
agree

598
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,960
to use the new material, newnium

599
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:28,320
in the factory's production lines

600
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:30,920
to create the patented glass,
Golden Years,

601
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:33,040
and supply it to all departments
that need it

602
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:34,080
for new products.

603
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:37,120
I bear sole responsibility
for all problems.

604
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:37,800
Note,

605
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:38,960
Usage of new materials

606
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:39,920
requires the signatures

607
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,000
and agreement from all related PICs.

608
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,120
Only then is this agreement

609
00:18:42,120 --> 00:18:43,240
in effect.

610
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,080
Both are needed.

611
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:45,000
PIC,

612
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,030
(PIC Signature: Jin Xiangyu)
Jin Xiangyu.

613
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:46,960
I've confirmed.

614
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,960
As do I.

615
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:50,150
(PIC Signature: He Jiahuan)
I've confirmed.

616
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,920
(PIC Signature: An Xiaowen)
Yeah, me as well.

617
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:52,880
Same here.

618
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,620
(PIC Signature: An Xiaoding)

619
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:56,100
(All four have signed the agreement
to use newnium)

620
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:56,880
What the hell is this?

621
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:58,480
Explain, now!

622
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:00,920
You dragged us into this!
We're innocent!

623
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,520
Honestly.

624
00:19:01,580 --> 00:19:02,980
(Helpless)

625
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:06,080
We have nothing

626
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,160
to explain.

627
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,280
Is this your signature?

628
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:10,560
I have never signed this.

629
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:11,640
Neither have I.

630
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:14,140
(They never signed this?)

631
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:15,600
We're framed!

632
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:16,520
(Cracked voice)
It wasn't them.

633
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:17,640
We don't remember

634
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:19,080
signing this.

635
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:22,100
(None remember signing the agreement)

636
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:25,600
An Er

637
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:27,000
sent me

638
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:29,000
the clothes from Goodcraft.

639
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:30,200
He needed

640
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,400
me to sign a contract.

641
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:33,380
(An Xiaoding has signed a contract
An Er brought him)

642
00:19:36,320 --> 00:19:37,040
Me too.

643
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:40,320
He Jiahuan and I were getting married.

644
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,080
He said

645
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:42,240
He wanted

646
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,520
a little checkup,

647
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:44,840
but the whole report was so long.

648
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:45,440
I didn't read it.

649
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:45,760
Yeah.

650
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:46,400
So I just signed it.

651
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,120
Me too.

652
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,880
He duped me into signing some document.

653
00:19:49,120 --> 00:19:49,440
And you?

654
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:50,960
Same thing.

655
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,200
He pulled something.

656
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,000
He...

657
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:55,480
He folded the corner of the agreement.

658
00:19:55,480 --> 00:19:56,040
My signature

659
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,480
went to this

660
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,400
agreement instead.

661
00:19:58,400 --> 00:20:00,000
That's the dirt he had on me.

662
00:20:00,100 --> 00:20:02,000
(He Jiahuan knew An Er used newnium)

663
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:04,120
He set me up.

664
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:05,120
Since I was a kid,

665
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:05,760
I've dreamt

666
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:07,640
of making the world know
of our nation's items.

667
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:09,520
(The Truth Weekly, He Jiahuan X An Xiaowen)
After joining the company,

668
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:11,680
(An Glass Factory gains technical expert SIL)
I slowly worked toward my dream.

669
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:12,600
(Another tech upgrade post An Songqiu's death)
But I noticed

670
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,120
ants dying from poison after licking

671
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,680
the glass.

672
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,960
I checked the glass

673
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,920
and found out a toxin called newnium

674
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,800
was added in.

675
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:22,880
(New material usage agreement)
Production said

676
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,080
I signed the papers.

677
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:25,680
Like hell I would!

678
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,680
(PIC Signature: He Jiahuan)
Then I remembered.

679
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:28,320
Only An Er came

680
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:29,600
to get my signature

681
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,440
I deduced that he

682
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,720
slid in that contract

683
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,240
to make me sign.

684
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,200
I confronted him.

685
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,320
Why'd you do that? I asked.

686
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,760
What do I care

687
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,480
about the consumers' wellbeing?

688
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,600
I'm going to be the chairman soon.

689
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:46,200
I don't need

690
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,720
your agreement for anything then.

691
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,720
Here I have it,

692
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,640
written in ink,

693
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,840
that I'm not the one

694
00:20:58,840 --> 00:20:59,520
who used newnium.

695
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:02,560
If this goes out
and the cops are involved,

696
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,880
I'll still be fine.

697
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,120
If you're smart,

698
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,240
you'll shut up.

699
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:13,480
That's why

700
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,040
(Husbando He)
I sought out Pai

701
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,920
and have her collect

702
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,840
dirt on An Er.

703
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,240
She managed to find it.

704
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,720
I think An Er is the best candidate

705
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,000
(Jin & An Yi's Room)
as chairman.

706
00:21:24,690 --> 00:21:26,120
I couldn't let scum like him take power.

707
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:28,240
That's his motive.

708
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:30,040
(He Jiahuan's motive: Had dirt,
lost place as heir)

709
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,040
So you knew toxin

710
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,440
was in there.

711
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,240
Not the time to talk

712
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,200
(Point is to return to ground)
about motives!

713
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,680
So we're framed!

714
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,720
An Er forged our signatures!

715
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,200
Yeah!

716
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:40,320
They're misunderstood.

717
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:41,560
They were duped into signing.

718
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:41,760
Yeah.

719
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:42,400
They didn't mean to.

720
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:43,760
We didn't sign.

721
00:21:43,760 --> 00:21:44,440
Didn't agree.

722
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:45,560
We'd never agree to that!

723
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:46,560
What a reprobate!

724
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:47,680
We're heirs

725
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,120
with a conscience!

726
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:51,560
So An Er duped all of you?

727
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:52,200
Yes.

728
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:52,600
Yeah.

729
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,560
It's a misunderstanding.

730
00:21:54,600 --> 00:21:55,080
See, if we

731
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,040
could talk it out,

732
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,120
we wouldn't have to hang.

733
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:58,000
I see.

734
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,280
Okay,

735
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:00,080
then it's all good.

736
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,360
Put us down.

737
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,960
You didn't take part

738
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:04,320
of the toxic glass' production,

739
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:05,240
but you

740
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:07,960
(Push Online reminds you)
signed without checking twice.

741
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:10,320
(to check closely before you sign)
That's indirect participation.

742
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:11,280
You'll be locked

743
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:13,720
for twenty-four hours

744
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:16,520
as a lesson.

745
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:17,400
What?

746
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:17,960
Come on.

747
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:18,480
Wait!

748
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:32,040
Our brother's dying!

749
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:32,480
No I'm not.

750
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:34,200
I just need some security.

751
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:35,900
(Hugs oversized self)

752
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:37,040
Any other ideas

753
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:38,400
to get down?

754
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,540
(Safety switch found. Container switch)

755
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:51,480
Where's the switch?

756
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:53,520
You can pull it down.

757
00:22:58,200 --> 00:22:58,880
We can pull it down.

758
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:00,160
How do we pull this?

759
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:00,840
Let's see.

760
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:01,840
If we pull this...

761
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:02,520
Hold on.

762
00:23:02,520 --> 00:23:03,360
Do we descend quick?

763
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,480
It's OK. Pull it.

764
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,920
3, 2, 1, go!

765
00:23:09,660 --> 00:23:11,300
(Why so formal?)

766
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:13,020
(Wha...)

767
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,360
Not a crash landing, huh?

768
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:15,280
Nah,

769
00:23:15,280 --> 00:23:16,240
that'd be too exciting.

770
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,320
I love it.

771
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:18,380
(Wen likes it)

772
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:18,960
Again!

773
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:19,240
Here.

774
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:20,880
(Going big)
3, 2, 1.

775
00:23:21,080 --> 00:23:21,280
Let's go!

776
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,840
What is this, strength training?

777
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:25,440
A workout?

778
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:26,680
Wait, wait.

779
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,280
Here.

780
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:28,400
(Master Ding disassembling)
Take this.

781
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,120
Take that.

782
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:30,400
Here.

783
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:31,680
Here.

784
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:32,960
3, 2, 1.

785
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,940
(Uncle and nephew stick together)

786
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:41,740
(Descending)

787
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:42,520
We survived.

788
00:23:43,060 --> 00:23:45,260
(Uncle Ke bouncing back
to top form soon)

789
00:23:46,180 --> 00:23:47,740
(Landing successful)

790
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:50,880
Door's still locked.

791
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,160
It's not opening.

792
00:23:53,460 --> 00:23:55,980
(Door is still locked)

793
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:57,000
Do something.

794
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,080
Can we take this glass off?

795
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:00,600
No way we can.

796
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:02,480
It must be really sturdy.

797
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,080
It won't open.

798
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,960
Hey, you think this is the exit?

799
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:16,820
(Escape exit?)

800
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:18,040
It's possible.

801
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,120
Maybe it's up there.

802
00:24:22,120 --> 00:24:23,080
Look, something's written here.

803
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:23,480
See?

804
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:24,640
Push...

805
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:27,100
(Push up hard)

806
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:28,520
Hard...

807
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:29,960
Push up hard!

808
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:30,840
Ning,

809
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:31,840
help us out!

810
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:32,480
Come on!

811
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,080
Here, I'll hold.

812
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,400
3, 2, 1, up!

813
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:36,960
Take that down.

814
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:37,320
Down.

815
00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:41,680
Put it here.

816
00:24:42,080 --> 00:24:42,440
Here.

817
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:44,800
Push up hard.

818
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:46,580
(Push up hard)

819
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:47,520
OK.

820
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:48,840
Look out.

821
00:24:48,840 --> 00:24:49,200
Sure.

822
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:49,680
I'll do it.

823
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:50,520
I'll do it.

824
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:52,340
(Ready to go)

825
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:53,680
Here.

826
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,760
3, 2, 1, go.

827
00:24:56,080 --> 00:24:56,680
Go!

828
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:57,760
Yep, yep.

829
00:24:59,160 --> 00:24:59,760
2, 3.

830
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:06,880
Take this and shove it up.

831
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:11,640
Don't crush his hand!

832
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:12,440
Here.

833
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:18,940
(Working together)

834
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:20,240
2, 1, go!

835
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:21,960
Yay!

836
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,600
Awesome!

837
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:24,760
Yay!

838
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,440
Awesome!

839
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,200
(Escape hatch opened)

840
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:26,760
Get down.

841
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:27,120
It's OK.

842
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:28,040
OK.

843
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:31,040
Freedom feels good.

844
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:33,600
Who'll go out?

845
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,800
We just need one to leave

846
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:39,960
and open the door.

847
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:43,300
(An Xiaoding suggests
sending one out and save the others)

848
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:43,960
Xiaoding's light.

849
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:45,520
Sure.

850
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:46,720
Xiaoding can go out first.

851
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,080
Really?

852
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:48,480
Yeah.

853
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,640
I'll take the clothes.

854
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,520
Makes it easier for you.

855
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:51,880
The edges

856
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,000
might cut you.

857
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:53,520
You...

858
00:25:53,520 --> 00:25:54,080
You should...

859
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:54,640
OK.

860
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:55,280
Just try it.

861
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:55,640
Yeah.

862
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:56,120
Okay.

863
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:56,480
Here.

864
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,080
Together.

865
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,520
3, 2, 1, go.

866
00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:00,880
OK, Xiaoding.

867
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:01,600
OK.

868
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,240
Careful.

869
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:05,280
OK.

870
00:26:05,280 --> 00:26:06,280
Take your time.

871
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:12,700
(An Xiaoding escapes)

872
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:13,800
Awesome!

873
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:14,160
